<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Elevated Route 53 API error rates>
We are currently investigating elevated error rates for some Route 53 API calls in the US-EAST-1 Region. There is no impact to answering DNS queries and they continue to work normally.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Elevated Route 53 API error rates>
Between 10:13 AM and 10:58 AM PDT we experienced intermittent elevated error rates for some Route 53 API calls in the US-EAST-1 Region. There was no impact to answering DNS queries throughout this time. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally
